    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embrace your primal instincts and step into the wild for a thrilling multiplayer game of tag where you and your friends become part of the animal kingdom! Outsmart your friends by using the landscape to your advantage, or work together to corner and capture your prey. Whether you're on the hunt or on the run, every round is packed with excitement and strategy. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Do you have what it takes to rise to the top of the animal kingdom?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293190/extras/c302eae9f070c63458f91b820fd80be7.poster.avif?t=1729817477\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293190/extras/c302eae9f070c63458f91b820fd80be7.webm?t=1729817477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293190/extras/c302eae9f070c63458f91b820fd80be7.mp4?t=1729817477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Fun: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join friends in online matches for up to 5 players.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Environments: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From lush meadows to icy mountain peaks, each map offers different challenges and opportunities for strategic gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock animals by completing themed challenges.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless Replayability: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each match is quick and full of adrenaline, making it easy to jump into another round for endless fun.</p>",
